    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736570/extras/f73759d90740d9a9abd6cbe4b9ad965f.avif?t=1669646351\" width=600 height=273 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Deflector: Specimen Zero</strong>是一款张力十足的roguelite游戏，你可以在游戏中改变层层弹幕的射击方向。投身实验，以最潇洒的方式根除致命病毒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736570/extras/c71e1af23c8b10ae7b427654d832df5d.poster.avif?t=1669646351\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736570/extras/c71e1af23c8b10ae7b427654d832df5d.webm?t=1669646351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736570/extras/c71e1af23c8b10ae7b427654d832df5d.mp4?t=1669646351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>身处枪林弹雨之中，进退两难之时，唯一出路就是反弹攻击！将投来之物悉数奉还，最终扭转弹幕炼狱的不利局面！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736570/extras/b1ffc775540f58003fc126176e25bb44.poster.avif?t=1669646351\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736570/extras/b1ffc775540f58003fc126176e25bb44.webm?t=1669646351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736570/extras/b1ffc775540f58003fc126176e25bb44.mp4?t=1669646351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>组合升级以解锁强势能力，并在自由加点的升级系统中发掘独特组合。使用残影、多重偏转抛射物炸飞敌人，甚至还可以破坏地面！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736570/extras/b9d4994ffa5a16dc9aa09a651414c6e1.poster.avif?t=1669646351\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"